{
  "stem": "3040.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're here already for two days, for three days, for a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But soon, things did start happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was living with my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was not married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met my wife before the war, but I was not married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not married at the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the very beginning, after maybe a week or two, we-- all kinds of ordinances appeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With regards to Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, the first order was that the Jews have to be identified by wearing the star of David on their arm-- on their left arm.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the order came that all Jewish stores and establishments have to be identified with a large star of David at the entrance, so that they knew right then which and where is a Jewish establishment and who is a Jew in the street.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because unlike the Poles, the Germans wouldn't be able to identify a Jew when you see him in the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Poles could differentiate between a Jew and a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they needed identification.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as we were wearing these armbands, things started to happen in the streets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were rounding up the Jews, putting them on trucks, and taking them someplace to do some work, some manual work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mostly cleaning work in the street work or cleaning up buildings, or this type of work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did you get assigned to?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if I was caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was not an assignment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At this time there was no requirement to report for work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this came very soon after this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the beginning, it was just-- they were rounding up people with armbands and taking them away on trucks, and then they let him go, and they could return home in the evenings after they were through.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
